Prerequisites
=============

To work on Castanet, you'll need Bundler ~> 1.0, RVM, and Ragel 6.7.  URLs:

http://gembundler.com
http://rvm.beginrescueend.com
http://www.complang.org/ragel

Once you've got Bundler, RVM, and Ragel installed and set up:

    $ bundle install
    $ rake udaeta:install_dependencies --trace   # because it helps to see what's going on
    $ rake ci --trace                            # ditto

To rebuild the state machines:

    $ rake fsm:rebuild


Build status and such
====================

